{
  "texts": [
    "In our view, and in line with the previous sections of this article, these acknowledgements should be incorporated into the publication of the actual resulting data sets, too.",
    "How should that be done?",
    "It is understandable that, due to administrative labour, larger projects in particular tend to acknowledge their volunteers in a more generalised manner, but there are also arguments in favour of listing members of the crowd as individuals in the case of Ground Truth publication.",
    "We want to provide three such arguments.",
    "First, choosing to name individuals is a more personal acknowledgement of their pivotal role in the data production process."
  ]
}